<h1>斩</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">zhǎn</span><span class=alesi>(zhan3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 斩 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 斩</h2><div class=abo>
